data.description: Welcome to this charming home nestled in the beautiful and mature Bittersweet neighborhood. This 1.5 story home boasts five spacious bedrooms, enclosed sun porch, upgraded kitchen featuring modern appliances and elegant finishes. A private primary suite with a loft area offering a versatile space for a home office or cozy reading nook. The spacious living room features a stunning floor to ceiling brick fireplace, and in the finished basement, you'll discover a cozy family room perfect for a recreational area or media room. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your forever home.
